"     <ol>",
"      <li>",
"       <span class=\"medCalcFontRef\">",
"        National High Blood Pressure Education Program Working Group on High Blood Pressure in Children and Adolescents.  The fourth report on the diagnosis, evaluation, and treatment of high blood pressure in children and adolescents.",
"        <i>",
"         Pediatrics",
"        </i>",
"        . 2004 Aug;114(2 Suppl 4th Report):555-76.",
"       </span>",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       <span class=\"medCalcFontRef\">",
"        Percentile conversion from Z-Score is done by table look-up in the standard Normal Table. Percentiles are provided for Z Scores between -3.09 and 3.09.  Values beyond these extremes return percentiles of 0.1 and 99.9 respectively.",
